description:
This week, Anna and Sim call Kelly Clarkson (MEANING OF LIFE, AMERICAN IDOL)! Kelly discusses how she handles fame (8:30), her pregnancy experience (14:00), and then answers some Deal-Breakers (16:00) and How Would Your Proceeds (26:30).

Later, Anna and Sim do some caller updates! First they call back Elizabeth (41:30) from the Lake Bell episode. Did she resolve her awkward situation with her boyfriend’s sister? Then they call Liana (51:00) from the Maria Bamford episode. Did her long term boyfriend pop the question?? Tune in to find out!!
